NK039(ti)036:1: // sa ma ya sa d+hu na ma di k+si d+ha bi dza ha ra ti sma ///
NK039(ti)036:2: dam can 'gar ba'i dbu phyogs legs so //
NK039(ti)036:4: bla ma gsang bdag rdo rje 'dzin //
NK039(ti)036:5: phyogs dus rgyal ba thams cad la //
NK039(ti)036:6: gnyis med gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK039(ti)036:7: dam can yid bzhin nor bu yi //
NK039(ti)036:8: bsnyen mchod bya thabs bri bar bya //
NK039(ti)036:9: de nas yi dam gyi bya ba gong du song nas /
NK039(ti)036:10: mdun du lcags mkhar nag po zur bzhi pa rgya
NK039(ti)036:11: che la 'pha' mtho ba dbu rtse ba dang ldan
NK039(ti)036:12: pa / phyi nang med pa me rlung 'tshubs pa /
NK039(ti)036:13: de'i dbus su bsgrub bya'i ro gan rkyal gyi steng du //
NK039(ti)036:14: ra skyes khams pa che la 'jigs pa /
NK039(ti)036:15: kha dang ba spu'i bu ga nas rin po che phyur ba /
NK039(ti)036:16: de'i gong du tri 'od du zhu ba las badz+ra sa d+hu sa ma y+aa rgyugs bring /
NK039(ti)036:17: thum ril dza dza b+ha ri b+ha ri dza dza
NK039(ti)036:18: sha la bam sha la bam dzahdzah king ka ri
NK039(ti)036:19: king ka ri dza dzah zhes brjod pas /
NK039(ti)036:20: dam can rdo rje legs pa /
NK039(ti)036:21: sku mdog sngo nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK039(ti)036:22: spyan gsum mche ba bzhi gtsigs pa /
NK039(ti)036:23: g.yas khro chu'i dgra s+t+wa dang /
NK039(ti)036:24: g.yon ra'i rgyal mtshan rin po che'i bkang ba bsnams pa /
NK039(ti)036:28: rgyab tu tho ba btsugs pa /
NK039(ti)036:29: thugs kar trihls rang sngags kyi bskor ba'o //
NK039(ti)036:31: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas dam can la phog /
NK039(ti)036:32: dam can gyi thugs ka'i sngags phreng las 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK039(ti)036:33: dregs pa can thams cad tshar bcad dbang du bsdus /
NK039(ti)036:34: ci 'dod pa'i dngos grub dang kho'i srog snying bdag la phul bar bsam /
NK039(ti)036:35: bsnyen pa yang skabs su bya g.yas su sha med gangs dkar ma seng ge la bcibs pa /
NK039(ti)036:36: g.yon du kha rag dpal mo btsun rgya stag la bcibs pa /
NK039(ti)036:37: rgyab tu kong btsun de mo bya mo nag mo la bcibs /
NK039(ti)036:38: g.yas su mon pa nag po bdud bya pho rog la bcibs pa /
NK039(ti)036:39: g.yon du mon ma nag mo gsod byed byi la ga pa la bcibs pa /
NK039(ti)036:40: de'i rgyab tu seng zhon gsum /
NK039(ti)036:45: sprel zhon gsum ra zhon gsum dang nyi shu rtsa gcig gis bskor ba /
NK039(ti)036:46: de'i rgyab tu mched 'khor sum brgya drug cu /
NK039(ti)036:47: de'i rgyab tu lha ma srin sde brgyad kyis bskor nas yod par bsam /
NK039(ti)036:49: bdag gi thugs ka'i trihls 'od zer 'phros gtsang 'o
NK039(ti)036:50: yug nas de 'dra ba spyan drangs la bstim mo
NK039(ti)036:51: spyi bor gtum po tshon gang ba gcig bsgom /
NK039(ti)036:52: bka' nyan gsung sdod cing ci bcol ba'i las byed par bsam mo //
NK039(ti)036:53: de nas ra gsur dang spos bsregs la 'di skad do //
NK039(ti)036:55: phyogs phyogs de ni pha we na //
NK039(ti)036:56: nyi ma nub phyogs pha we na //
NK039(ti)036:57: zangs lcags 'dres pa'i mkhar nang nas //
NK039(ti)036:58: sde brgyad yongs kyi spyi bo'i rje //
NK039(ti)036:59: pha ni mon pa nag po yin //
NK039(ti)036:60: ma ni mon ma nag mo yin //
NK039(ti)036:61: bu dam can rdo rje legs pa ni //
NK039(ti)036:62: zhal gcig phyag gnyis brjid pa'i sku //
NK039(ti)036:63: sku la dar ber dgu brtsegs gsol //
NK039(ti)036:64: gser ka rin chen sku rags bcings //
NK039(ti)036:65: zhabs la sag ti lhwam po che //
NK039(ti)036:66: dbu la sag zhu dmar smug gsol //
NK039(ti)036:67: g.yas pas khro chu'i dgra sta phyar //
NK039(ti)036:68: g.yon pas ra yi rgyal mtshan bsnams //
NK039(ti)036:69: stag ral g.yas la gzigs shubs g.yon //
NK039(ti)036:70: ya tsha dkar po glog ltar 'gyur //
NK039(ti)036:71: zangs gri dmar po rked du mdzes //
NK039(ti)036:72: chibs su ra skyes kham pa bcibs //
NK039(ti)036:73: g.yas na sha med gangs dkar ma //
NK039(ti)036:74: seng ge bcibs shing gtso la 'dud //
NK039(ti)036:75: g.yon du kha rag dpal mo btsun //
NK039(ti)036:76: rgya stag zhon nas gtso la stobs //
NK039(ti)036:77: rgyab tu kong btsun de mo ni //
NK039(ti)036:78: bya mo bcibs shing gtso la 'dud //
NK039(ti)036:79: g.yas su mon pa nag po ni //
NK039(ti)036:80: bdud bya pho rog chibs su cibs //
NK039(ti)036:81: g.yon du mon ma nag mo ni //
NK039(ti)036:82: gsod byed byi la ga pa bcibs //
NK039(ti)036:83: yab yum pho mo sras 'khor bcas //
NK039(ti)036:84: mched 'khor sum brgya drug cu dang //
NK039(ti)036:85: yongs 'khor lha srin sde brgyad rnams //
NK039(ti)036:86: ma lus gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)036:87: rgyan gyi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)036:88: rnal 'byor bdag cag bsgrub pa po //
NK039(ti)036:89: 'khor bsrung rkyen bzlog dkor nor srung //
NK039(ti)036:90: mi sdug dgra la cho 'phrul thod //
NK039(ti)036:91: bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)036:92: 'dod pa'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK039(ti)036:93: khyod la mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)036:94: mi dang ra yi gsur dud dang //
NK039(ti)036:95: 'dzam bu gling gi zas kyi mchog /
NK039(ti)036:96: sngon mo nas kyis snying khu der //
NK039(ti)036:97: rin chen dam pa gser skyems nas //
NK039(ti)036:98: dam can khyod la mchod pa 'bul //
NK039(ti)036:99: ra yi dbang po rnam lnga dang //
NK039(ti)036:100: bla mkhar smug po'i logs la tri ra dang pho rog byi li'i snying //
NK039(ti)036:101: zangs khab za 'og sna tshogs dang //
NK039(ti)036:102: gser dngul g.yu dang mu tig dang //
NK039(ti)036:103: dung dang bye ru zangs lcags dang //
NK039(ti)036:104: mda' dar me long dar sna dang //
NK039(ti)036:105: bka' yi gtor ma rgyan can dang //
NK039(ti)036:106: nyams pa bsgral ba'i sha khrag 'di //
NK039(ti)036:107: dam can khyod la mchod pa 'bul //
NK039(ti)036:108: khyod la phrin las bcol ba ni //
NK039(ti)036:109: bdag cag rnal byor bsgrub pa po //
NK039(ti)036:110: phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad gar 'gro yang //
NK039(ti)036:111: sa phyogs gang du bsdad pa'i sar //
NK039(ti)036:112: btsan grogs longs spyod ldan pa dang //
NK039(ti)036:113: bstan pa dar zhing rgyas pa dang //
NK039(ti)036:114: za kha grol zhing dkor nor spel //
NK039(ti)036:115: bu rta na tsha mi 'ong zhing //
NK039(ti)036:116: ci bsam don rnams 'grub pa yi //
NK039(ti)036:117: sdong grogs rgyab brten khyed kyis mdzod //
NK039(ti)036:118: khyed la snga ma'i gtang rag dang //
NK039(ti)036:120: yul du 'dug na yul dpon gyis //
NK039(ti)036:121: byes su 'gro na byas dpon gyis //
NK039(ti)036:122: ngan dang bsnol la bzang dang sprod //
NK039(ti)036:123: khyod la rtag tu las bcol na //
NK039(ti)036:124: bdag la brnyas byed sdig can dang //
NK039(ti)036:125: nyams pa can gyi dgra bo 'di //
NK039(ti)036:126: dam can dmag dpung 'khor bcas kyis //
NK039(ti)036:127: srog gcod snying phyungs 'byung bzhi sprugs //
NK039(ti)036:128: me dbal gag lhog gzer gsum sogs //
NK039(ti)036:129: tsha nad 'brum pa lhog gam rims //
NK039(ti)036:130: srog snying dkrug pa'i nad rnams kyis //
NK039(ti)036:131: gtan nas brlag pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK039(ti)036:132: gal te dam la khyod 'da' nas //
NK039(ti)036:133: mngag pa bzhin du ma byas na //
NK039(ti)036:134: sngon gyi dam tshig nyams gyur pas //
NK039(ti)036:135: dus la mi 'da' phrin las mdzod //
NK039(ti)036:136: badz+ra sa d+hu sa ma y+aa /
NK039(ti)036:137: rgyug bring thum ril dza dza /
NK039(ti)036:138: b+ha ri b+ha ri dza dza /
NK039(ti)036:139: sha la bam sha la bam dza dzah king ka
NK039(ti)036:140: ri king ka ri dza dzah e dam b+ha ling
NK039(ti)036:142: mchod cig pha mon pa nag po /
NK039(ti)036:144: bu dam can mgar ba nag po /
NK039(ti)036:149: yang 'khor lha srin sde brgyad dang bcas pa rnams
NK039(ti)036:150: kyi zhal du bka' yi gtor ma rgyan gyis mchod
NK039(ti)036:152: sdang byed kyi dgra bo sod /
NK039(ti)036:155: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srung /
NK039(ti)036:157: rdo rje slob dpon gyi sku tshe bsrings /
NK039(ti)036:158: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu rdul du barloga /
NK039(ti)036:159: mi mthun pa'i phyogs ngan pa thams cad zhi ba dang /
NK039(ti)036:160: dul ba dang bzlog pa dang /
NK039(ti)036:161: med pa tshad bcad pa'i phrin las mdzod cig /
NK039(ti)036:163: thugs ka'i sngags phreng las 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK039(ti)036:164: dregs pa thams cad tshar bcad nas /
NK039(ti)036:165: bdag la ci 'dod pa'i dngos grub thob pa bsam /
NK039(ti)036:167: zhes pa'ang kahthoga rdo rje'i gdan gyis longs khrod du shi la ke tu'i sbyar ba'o //
NK039(ti)036:168: badz+ra sa d+hu sa ma ya /
NK039(ti)036:171: sh+ri tri mi li h+r+ai tri a dkar sha ya rat+na 'dus 'dus dbang du 'dus /
NK039(ti)036:172: srid pa gsum gyi skad cha nga la shod //
NK039(ti)036:173: zas nor longs spyod dngos grub bdag la rtsol //
NK039(ti)036:174: badz+ra sa d+hu sa ma y+aa /
NK039(ti)036:175: rdo rje 'bar ba has byas hus byas tsit+ta a
